msg: LENS-538: Fix java6 compilation failure after LENS-486
LENS-537: Fixes test case failures in QueryAPIErrorResponseTest caused due to unspecified date locale
LENS-256 : lens-cli should not use single parameter for two values (Rajat Khandelwal via amareshwari)
LENS-176 : Lens server should support API to retrieve and update expression columns with multiple expressions (amareshwari)
LENS-186 : Add Session lifecycle events and session metrics (Raju Bairishetti via amareshwari)
LENS-545 : Remove duplicate declaration of guava dependency in lens-cube pom ( Yash Sharma via amareshwari)
LENS-544: Fixes failure of TestExprColumn due to time zone not being set
LENS-548 : Remove no-prefix and -p0 from contribute doc (Yash Sharma via amareshwari)
LENS-198 : Allow timed dimensions of cube to be non-partitioned columns as well (Rajat Khandelwal via amareshwari)
LENS-546 : change parameter names to have _ instead of - in cli arg names (Yash Sharma via amareshwari)
